modules.description: Generates and manipulates HTML5 and SVG elements using a type-safe approach, supporting both standard HTML syntax and JSX through PPX. It works with custom element types, attributes, and event handlers, ensuring structural correctness at compile time. Used to construct dynamic web content with guaranteed valid markup in OCaml applications.

Checks if an expression is JSX syntax, converts string casing, and manipulates XML-like structures. Processes OCaml AST expressions, attributes, and element lists for JSX transformation. Extracts and modifies attributes, elements, and component definitions during code generation.
